{"build_type":"library","description":"Return 1 if the parameter linked-list starting at member contains a parameter whose parameter_name is __argv, else 0. Walks .next. Used to decide whether a tool entry can carry the describe prologue (which reads argv); entries without __argv, e.g. reconcile, are skipped so the prologue never references a missing parameter. Reuses locate_named_member_inside_mapping, compare_two_strings_byte_by_byte.","module_name":"entry-arguments-include-vector-identifier","package_name":"entry-arguments-include-vector-identifier","function_definitions":{"entry-arguments-include-vector-identifier":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"member","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_pn","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"parameter_name"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_argv","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"__argv"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"!=","lhs":{"value":"member"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"locate-named-member-inside-mapping","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"member"},{"kind":"var","value":"s_pn"}],"result_assignment_variable":"pn","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"fetch-string-field-tolerating-absence","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"pn"}],"result_assignment_variable":"pnv","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name"